<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 17pt;"><b><i><u><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;"> </span></u></i></b></p>
 
<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; text-indent: 17pt;"><img width="453" height="223" src="file:///C:/Users/STEPAN~1/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image004.jpg"  /> 
